title: Windows 11 build 22616 is out for Insiders with fixes
content:
Today, Microsoft is releasing Windows 11 Insider Preview build 22616 to the Dev and Beta channels. Unfortunately, there really isn’t anything of note that’s new. It contains some fixes, but that’s about it. The big thing to talk about is that if you’re on the Dev channel, it’s still time to reconsider your channels. At

description: Microsoft has released this week's Windows 11 Insider Preview ring to the Dev and Beta channels, but there are no new features.
